PresentationTable.name: More Office Objects
PresentationTable.Description: -> This folder contains additional Office attributes.

PresentationColumn.name: Office Key
PresentationColumn.Description: Office Key is an integer that uniquely identifies each record in the Offices dimension table.

PresentationColumn.name: Org Key
PresentationColumn.Description: Surrogate key for the Organization objects.

PresentationColumn.name: Dept Key
PresentationColumn.Description: Surrogate key for the Department objects.

PresentationColumn.name: Company Key
PresentationColumn.Description: Surrogate key for the Company objects.

PresentationColumn.name: Office Sequence
PresentationColumn.Description: This column returns the Office sequence from the Offices Dimension, the office sequence is used to logically sort the Office object values.
